- Fixed LV2 plugin buffersize setting in case of smaller
  internal buffersize.

2015-9-14 Will
- Fixed bug that let an invalid instrument be stored in a bank.
- Changed 'Parameters' to 'Patch sets'
- Set version as 1.3.6 rc4.

